data.description: Introducing this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, complete with a pool and covered patio. Nestled in a sought after neighborhood, this residence exudes comfort and a relaxed atmosphere. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open and airy living space. The interior features tasteful updates, wood floors and beautiful tile floors in the kitchen. There is a separate formal dining and second den area with bar area perfect for entertaining family and friends. The outdoor space is centered around an inground pool and the covered patio offers a shaded area for relaxation and outdoor dining, creating the perfect setting for gatherings. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
